<interface>ICanvas</interface><method> DrawArc </method>
    <description>
        <para>
            绘制拱形。
        </para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> ECode </return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32 </param_type>
                <param_name> x </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
绘制的拱形的左上角的x坐标                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32 </param_type>
                <param_name> y </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
绘制的拱形的左上角的y坐标                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32 </param_type>
                <param_name> radius </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
绘制的拱形的半径                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32 </param_type>
                <param_name> startAngle </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
绘制的拱形的起始角度                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32 </param_type>
                <param_name> angleSpan </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
绘制的拱形弧度。即角度跨辐                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Color </param_type>
                <param_name> color </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
用来绘制拱形的画笔的颜色，颜色的取值指定为<link url="../../datatype/ColorChart.htm">ColorChart</link>数据类型。</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

<return>
    <para>
            如果方法调用成功，则返回NOERROR；如果有参数无效，则方法调用失败，并返回E_INVALID_ARGUMENT 。    </para>
</return>
    <requirements>
        <system>
            <system_name>
Elastos操作系统            </system_name>
        </system>
        <headerfile>
            <file_name>ElGrafix.h</file_name>
        </headerfile>
        <library>
            <lib_name>elastos.lib</lib_name>
        </library>
    </requirements>    
</manpage>